      "date": "2013-02-17 17:16:38.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/f0daf9b6-791c-11e2-9a74-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  6 tests failed: sanity-quota, replay-ost-single, conf-sanity, replay-single, sanityn, sanity.",
